snippet.title: Wayward Strand | Teaser | Ida's Visitor
snippet.description:
A short teaser video, in which Casey, Wayward Strand's player character, meets one of the airship's residents.

You can now add Wayward Strand to your Wishlist on Steam! Visit https://store.steampowered.com/app/1080450/Wayward_Strand.

You can see more about Wayward Strand at https://waywardstrand.com.
